{
  "texts": [
    "Motivation.",
    "In this scenario, we train a pretrained model directly with alignment methods on the UltraFeedback dataset.",
    "Several motivations underlie this scenario.",
    "Firstly, we seek to determine whether alignment methods necessitate the SFT phase.",
    "Secondly, we aim to compare the performance of models aligned with DPO, CPO, KTO, and IPO against those trained with SFT."
  ]
}